data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Pooler, Georgia! This charming single-story residence nestled in the sought-after Somersby neighborhood offers the epitome of comfort and convenience. Boasting 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a versatile flex room with elegant double glass doors, this home caters to every lifestyle need. Step into your own private oasis with a fenced yard, complete with a screened porch and extended patio, all set against a serene wooded backdrop-ideal for hosting gatherings or simply enjoying peaceful moments outdoors. Inside, the well-maintained interior welcomes you with open arms, showcasing a thoughtfully designed kitchen featuring granite countertops, a spacious island and pantry perfect for culinary adventures and entertaining guests with ease. Conveniently located near Pooler Parkway and I-16, this home offers seamless access to amenities, shopping, dining, and more. Dont miss the opportunity to make this residence your own-schedule your viewing today!
